						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Viśvāvasu</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers the gift of gold by Āṟkāḍukiḻāṉ Śīraṅganāthaṉ a <hi rend="italic">cheṭṭiyār</hi> of Maṇṇaikoṇḍachōḷa-Madurāntakapuram to run a service of food offerings in his name as Āṟkāḍukiḻān-sandhi, during the nights at the close of the usual service. The details of the date viz., <hi rend="bold">Visvāvaśu, Āḍi, 20,</hi> are insufficient for verification. The record is in late characters.</p>						

						</summary>
